https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qj2oDkvc4dQ
https://docs.mongodb.com/compass/master/install/
1. crate a project folder in Desktop or anywhere
2. npm init
3. install 'npm install express'
4. install 'npm install express-handlebars'
5. create folder and files (https://www.npmjs.com/package/express-handlebars) 
    ├── app.js
    └── views
        ├── home.handlebars
        └── layouts
            └── main.handlebars

        2 directories, 3 files

6. install 'mongodb' & 'mongodb compass'
7. connect mondodb and the project